            "text": {
                "content": "<p>When a creature makes an Attack, it can do so by choosing a target within the Attack\u2019s Range (Melee or Ranged) and by making a Check (Attack or Spell). How the Attack is resolved is determined by its Type and its Range.</p>",
                "format": 1
