            "name": "Martial Attacks",
            "ownership": {
                "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3,
                "default": -1
            },
            "sort": 4,
            "src": null,
            "system": {},
            "text": {
                "content": "<p>A creature makes a Martial Attack when it makes an Attack Check using a Weapon or Unarmed Strike against a target\u2019s Defense.</p><p><strong><em>Unarmed Strike: </em></strong>A Martial Attack made using any part of a creature\u2019s own body, such as a punch, elbow, kick, knee, or headbutt.</p><p><strong><em>Weapon Attack: </em></strong>A Martial Attack made using a Weapon, such as an Axe, Sword, or Bow. You can draw a Weapon as part of an Attack made using it.</p>",
                "format": 1
            },
            "title": {
                "level": 3,
                "show": true
            },
            "type": "text",
            "video": {
                "controls": true,
                "volume": 0.5
